T02TD1611E:101b-41: rdo rje'i lag can de bzhin gzhu //
T02TD1611E:101b-42: rdo rje chen po bde ba che //
T02TD1611E:101b-43: las kun rjes su sgrub byed ma //
T02TD1611E:101b-44: sbyor pa'i dkyil 'khong rgyal po che //
T02TD1611E:101b-45: de bzhin rdo rje dbang phyug gtso//
T02TD1611E:101b-46: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku chen te //
T02TD1611E:101b-48: rdo rje'i dbang mo bka' yis ni //
T02TD1611E:101b-49: thams cad kun nas 'dir byon cig / kha khkh'a da na sarba dusht'a na ha na ha na /
T02TD1611E:101b-50: gh'a ta ya gh'a ta ya /
T02TD1611E:101b-52: ai dam karma s'a dha ya h'um h'um h'um phat phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1611E:102a-0: de nas nyer spyod lnga rnams @102a * //
T02TD1611E:102a-2: / mnyam par gzhag ste mchod par bya //
T02TD1611E:102a-3: rdo rje dril bu bzung gyur pas //
T02TD1611E:102a-4: lha rnams thams cad mnyes par bya //
T02TD1611E:102a-5: deng bdag sems dpa' chen po mchog / dga' ba chen po mgu ba che //
T02TD1611E:102a-6: kun du bzang po kun gyi bdag / rdo rje snyems ma'i bdag po'i bdag /
T02TD1611E:102a-7: thugs kyi rdo rje ting 'dzin mchog / rdo rje sems dpa' stobs po cha //
T02TD1611E:102a-8: kun du bzang po spyod pa'i mchog / bdud ni gsod cing 'joms par byed //
T02TD1611E:102a-9: kun du khros shing byang chub che //
T02TD1611E:102a-10: sangs rgyas byang chub mchog tu 'khrungs //
T02TD1611E:102a-11: mchog skyes rdo rje h'um mdzad de //
T02TD1611E:102a-13: 'dod chags chen po bde ba che //
T02TD1611E:102a-14: 'dod dang thar pa'i nor che ba //
T02TD1611E:102a-15: lus gsum srid gsum mchog gsum ste //
T02TD1611E:102a-16: 'jig rten gsum mchog khams gsum pa //
T02TD1611E:102a-17: brtan pa yi ni mchog tu gsal //
T02TD1611E:102a-18: shin tu phra dang sbom pa'i tshogs //
T02TD1611E:102a-19: g-yob yi ni rab mchog brnyes //
T02TD1611E:102a-20: srid pa 'khor ba sbyong mdzad pa //
T02TD1611E:102a-21: thog ma tha ma bar ma med //
T02TD1611E:102a-22: thams cad kyi ni thog mar gnas //
T02TD1611E:102a-23: snying po phyag rgya rnal 'byor dang //
T02TD1611E:102a-24: mchod chen de nyid dam tshig nyid //
T02TD1611E:102a-25: rdo rje khro bo khro ba che //
T02TD1611E:102a-26: gsal bar smra ba ster ba po //
T02TD1611E:102a-27: gdug pa'i mchog ni 'dul ba che //
T02TD1611E:102a-28: drag shul gzugs can 'jigs par byed //
T02TD1611E:102a-29: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dngos grub che //
T02TD1611E:102a-30: chos dang las dang stobs che ba //
T02TD1611E:102a-31: dam chos dam pa'i las kyi lam //
T02TD1611E:102a-32: byang chub sems ni rnam sbyong byed //
T02TD1611E:102a-33: thams cad dag pa'i padma che //
T02TD1611E:102a-34: shes rab thabs kyi nor che ba //
T02TD1611E:102a-35: 'dod chags dag pa'i ting 'dzin mchog / sna tshogs chags pa'i dbang phyug che //
T02TD1611E:102a-36: nam mkha' mtha' yas rtag pa'i don //
T02TD1611E:102a-37: sems can kun gyi stobs chen po //
T02TD1611E:102a-39: bsam pa thams cad rdzogs mdzad ma //
T02TD1611E:102a-41: bdag nyid dad pas khyod la 'dud //
T02TD1611E:102a-42: deng bdag rdo rje sems grub mdzod //
T02TD1611E:102a-43: ces pas dril bu dkrol bar bya //
T02TD1611E:102a-44: zhes pa gtor ma'i cho ga'o //
T02TD1611E:102a-45: sngar bzhin mchod pa thams cad kyis //
T02TD1611E:102a-46: khyad par du ni mchod par bya //
T02TD1611E:102a-47: yi ge brgya pa'i sngags kyis kyang //
T02TD1611E:102a-48: lan gsum brjod pas bzod par gsol //
T02TD1611E:102b-0: khyad @102b par du ni mkha' 'gro mas //
T02TD1611E:102b-1: sngags dman pa dang bya ba dman //
T02TD1611E:102b-2: de kun bzod par mdzad du gsol //
T02TD1611E:102b-3: mchod pa byas nas gdan rnams kyang //
T02TD1611E:102b-4: thams cad lus la gnas par bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-5: bza' dang bca' dang de bzhin du //
T02TD1611E:102b-6: btung ba rnams kyang tshim par btung //
T02TD1611E:102b-7: bdud rtsi'i snod ni bkang na ni //
T02TD1611E:102b-8: nyi ma'i lag par gzhag par bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-9: rnam shes ming med dag gis ni //
T02TD1611E:102b-10: sngags pa yis ni bsrung bar bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-11: de la 'di ni gsang sngags te //
T02TD1611E:102b-12: aom ha ho:hr'i:shr'im h'um a'a:sv'a h'a //
T02TD1611E:102b-13: lcags kyu yi ni rnam pa rnams //
T02TD1611E:102b-14: bye brag tu ni rnam pa lnga //
T02TD1611E:102b-15: zla bar snod ni yang dag bzhag / nyi ma'i lag pas sbyang bar bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-16: de la 'di ni gsang sngags te //
T02TD1611E:102b-17: shr'im h'um ghram h'um a'a:sv'a h'a /
T02TD1611E:102b-18: las kyi rdo rje cho ga shes //
T02TD1611E:102b-19: lcags kyu'i snod ni dbul bar bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-21: de nyid ldan pas dbul bar bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-22: padma'i snod ni bzung nas ni //
T02TD1611E:102b-23: bdud rtsi'i bcud kyis rab tu dgang //
T02TD1611E:102b-24: tshigs bcad sngags dang phyag rgya brjod //
T02TD1611E:102b-25: ngo bo kun la dbul bar bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-26: 'di rnams chos rnams bzang por ltos //
T02TD1611E:102b-27: 'dus pa rnams la the tshom med //
T02TD1611E:102b-28: bram ze khyi dang gdol pa rnams //
T02TD1611E:102b-29: rang bzhin gcig pa nyid du rol //
T02TD1611E:102b-30: de ltar rnam rig rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1611E:102b-31: padma'i bsko rang sngon du bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-32: nyi ma yi ni padma bzung //
T02TD1611E:102b-33: zla bas rdo rje sbyar bar bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-34: de nyid rnal 'byor pas bzung ste //
T02TD1611E:102b-35: tshigs bcad 'di ni brjod par bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-36: bde gshegs chos la rin thang med //
T02TD1611E:102b-37: 'dod chags la sogs dri ma spangs //
T02TD1611E:102b-38: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam bral ba //
T02TD1611E:102b-39: de kho na nyid gus phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1611E:102b-40: deng nas bzung ste rnal 'byor bdag / legs par mnyam gzhag bsgom par bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-41: nyi ma'i lag pa dgod pa ni //
T02TD1611E:102b-43: yi ge nyis 'gyur gsang sngags ni //
T02TD1611E:102b-44: thig le dang ldan kun nas 'bar //
T02TD1611E:102b-45: zla phyed dang mtshungs snod da bus su //
T02TD1611E:102b-46: zla ba'i dngos po dang 'dra bar //
T02TD1611E:102b-47: aom yig dbus su dgod par bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-48: rnam pa lnga yis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1611E:102b-49: ming med mthe bong rdo rje yis //
T02TD1611E:102b-50: yi ge rnams ni bsrub par bya //
T02TD1611E:102b-51: sbos ma la sogs sngags gsum gyis //
T02TD1611E:102b-52: lha mo gsum ni rnam par bsgom //
T02TD1611E:102b-53: de yi lce yi rtse mo dang//
T02TD1611E:103a-0: @103a * // snying ga spyi bo dpral bar dbul //
T02TD1611E:103a-1: phyi nas ji ltar bde bar bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-2: gzhan dang gzhan la'ang blta bya zhing //
T02TD1611E:103a-3: de ltar gzhan dang gzhan tshim bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-4: tha mal nga rgyal mi bya zhing //
T02TD1611E:103a-5: shes rab thabs kyi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1611E:103a-6: lha rnams dran par bya ba mchog / ji ltar bde bas bde ba ni //
T02TD1611E:103a-7: ji ltar 'dod bzhin gnas par bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-8: spro dang bsdu ba'i dngos po rnams //
T02TD1611E:103a-9: gang tshe dus su gshegs gsol bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-10: sbyang par bya ba'i las gang zhig / gtor ma snod du bsams nas ni //
T02TD1611E:103a-11: nyer spyod lnga yis mchod par bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-12: dang por dri la sogs pas mchod //
T02TD1611E:103a-13: kha ni bdud rtsis bkang nas ni //
T02TD1611E:103a-14: snod kyi nang du blugs par bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-15: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis bcings nas //
T02TD1611E:103a-16: dkar po gi wang bsgreng bar bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-17: de yi rtse mo gnyis bskul nas //
T02TD1611E:103a-18: kha yi ngos su gzhag par bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-19: sa gdugs padma'i sor mo gnyis //
T02TD1611E:103a-20: kha ru bcug ste gzhag par bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-21: dud sol ma yi phyag rgya che //
T02TD1611E:103a-22: sdang ba thams cad 'gugs par byed //
T02TD1611E:103a-23: aom gu ru ru batt'a li //
T02TD1611E:103a-25: siddhi mu kham sma sh'a ni pa si ni pe ta mu khe /
T02TD1611E:103a-27: tsanda ka r'a l'i ni sa ma yo rakshi te /
T02TD1611E:103a-32: ma dhye bhundza[?] ha bhaksha ha /
T02TD1611E:103a-33: sa ha ga na du ta /
T02TD1611E:103a-35: ti shtha sva ku ru ku ru /
T02TD1611E:103a-36: grihna grihna grihna h'um h'um h'um /
T02TD1611E:103a-44: bzhi mdo dang ni gshin rje'i nag / ri dang shing gcig chu klung cher //
T02TD1611E:103a-45: nyer spyod lnga yis mchod nas ni //
T02TD1611E:103a-46: se gol gsum ni brdab par bya //
T02TD1611E:103a-47: aom khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
T02TD1611E:103a-48: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
T02TD1611E:103a-49: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
T02TD1611E:103a-50: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
T02TD1611E:103a-51: aom a'a:badzra mu:sems can kun dang srog chags kun //
T02TD1611E:103a-52: khyed cag bde dang ldan gyur cig / sems can thams cad nad med pa //
T02TD1611E:103a-53: gang gis lam gyis 'gro ba yis //
T02TD1611E:103a-54: sangs rgyas nyid ni myur thob shog / ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi //
T02TD1611E:103a-55: ma grol ba rnams bdag gis dgrol //
T02TD1611E:103a-56: de ltar rjes su brtse bzhin pas //
T02TD1611E:103a-57: rnal 'byor bstan bcos bdag gis bgyi'o //
T02TD1611E:103b-0: de nas rdo rje khu tshur @103b snying gar bzhag ste //
T02TD1611E:103b-1: nyi ma'i lag pa brkyang nas gzhag par bya'o //
T02TD1611E:103b-2: aom gatstsha gatstsha bhur bhu wa na sva:sv'a h'a /
T02TD1611E:103b-3: zhes brjod nas 'jig rten las 'das pa rnams gshegs su gsol bar bya'o //
T02TD1611E:103b-4: de nas 'jig rten pa rnams ni /
T02TD1611E:103b-7: gatstsha pu n'a r'a ga ma n'a ya h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1611E:103b-9: se gol gsum brdabs nas gshegs su gsol bar bya'o zhes pa gdan bzhi chen po'i rgyud kyi rgyal po las phyung ba //
T02TD1611E:103b-10: bdag gi gdan dpal rnal 'byor nam mkha'i sgrub thabs kyi cho ga / bla ma dam pa rnams kyi man ngag ltar shin tu rgyas par bkod cing /
T02TD1611E:103b-11: sgrub thabs 'bring po dang bsdus pa yang shugs las rtogs par 'gyur bas rmad du byung ba'i gdams pa 'di ni mal po'i pandi ta chen po dza ga ta a'a nanda dz'i ba bha dras mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1611E:103b-13: // / sgrub thabs 'di nyid dang mthun pa'i bka' lung sngan chad bod du mi snang ba las //
T02TD1611E:103b-14: dza gata a'a nanda'i sras kyi thu bo //
T02TD1611E:103b-15: pandi ta ma h'a bo dhi las legs par mnos shing //
T02TD1611E:103b-16: bka' lung mi 'chad par bya ba'i don du /
T02TD1611E:103b-17: pandi ta'i phyag nas rgya dpe gdan drang zhing //
T02TD1611E:103b-18: bka' lung don du gnyer ba mang pos kyang gsol ba 'debs pa'i ngor //
T02TD1611E:103b-19: gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa'i bka' lung man ngag du mas nye bar spras pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dam pa bla ma 'phags pa'i bkas bskul ba la brten nas khams gsum gyi bla ma dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo chos kyi rje /
T02TD1611E:103b-20: bod kyi pandi ta ma ti dhva dza shr'i bha dra dang /
T02TD1611E:103b-21: dpal ldan byang chub rtse mo'i bka' drin gyis bskyangs pa'i lo ts'a ba'i ming tsam 'dzin pa dpal ldan smra ba'i seng ges tshig dang don gyi cha la legs par dpyad nas /
T02TD1611E:103b-22: dpal sa skya'i gtsug lag khang chen por legs par bsgyur ba'o//
